      <h1 class="text-2xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-[var(--ink)] leading-tight">What Is Operating Software? How Modern Businesses Leverage AI-Driven Automation for Efficiency</h1>
      <p class="text-[var(--ink-mute)] mt-4 text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed">Operating software is the backbone of modern business infrastructure. This guide explains what it is, how Enterprise Operating Systems structure workflows, how AI agents join the team as full members, and how the OTP platform brings it together for EOS teams.</p>
